Command to run valgrind
valgrind --leak-check=full ./bst
Replace ./bst with your executable.

Make sure you compile your code with the -g option. See the Makefile in this directory as an example.

To run gdb
gdb ./bst
gdb commands
r: runs your code within gdb
bt: backtrace displays the contents of the stack. Usually good to trace which function calls led to a segfault.
